INSERT INTO segment (
                    id,
                    name,
                    distance,
                    average_grade,
                    maximum_grade,
                    elevation_high,
                    elevation_low,
                    start_lat,
                    start_long,
                    end_lat,
                    end_long,
                    climb_category,
                    city,
                    state,
                    country,
                    activity_type,
                    hazardous
                ) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
                ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING
